  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/hdtv/\" rel=\"tag\">高清电视</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/industry/\" rel=\"tag\">产业新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/25/nikkei-sony-to-end-oled-tv-partnership/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/8543d5a9b2b32b9c62eb8a315f08349f/panasonic-sony-oled-ending-2013-12-25-02.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n日经新闻今天报道称，去年<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2012/05/15/panasonic-sony-oled/\">抱团取暖</a>、共谋 OLED 大计的索尼和松下很快将走到感情的尽头。据悉合作破裂的原因是双方无法联手造出耐用且俱有价格竞争力的产品，因而两大日系巨头选择了在今年合同到期后分道扬镳。至于接下来的发展重点，他们不约而同选择了刚刚兴起的 4K 市场（据 DisplaySearch 统计去年 4K 产品的销量达到了 195 万台）。如果是这样的话，那在即将于两周内开始的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/ces2014\">CES 2014</a> 上应该会出现更多的新款 4K 电视，不过想普及的话还是要价格给力啊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/12/25/nikkei-sony-to-end-oled-tv-partnership/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://news.oled-display.net/sony-and-panasonic-stop-their-oled-tv-partnership/\" target=\"_blank\">OLED-Display.Net</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://asia.nikkei.com/Business/Companies/Technical-difficulties-foil-Sony-Panasonic-OLED-effort\" target=\"_blank\">Nikkei</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/25/nikkei-sony-to-end-oled-tv-partnership/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20795297/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/25/nikkei-sony-to-end-oled-tv-partnership/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
